    <TargetNodeGuid>k__BackingField: ac8f7ab0-626a-4f8e-9be2-c796139b2b72
  <DialogueNodeData>k__BackingField:
  - guid: 7e7e1564-0955-4847-9509-02c9435758e4
    dialogue: []
    position: {x: 100, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 0
    entryPoint: 1
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 4c27de3a-4fea-461e-bb66-a38f7e3f098c
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Hello co-worker. I am Katoro. Please do not be afraid.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: I do not want to hurt you. It's just how they programmed
        me.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 269.5, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 91a1f160-0a63-4b8a-b74d-aed94a12cd92
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Is this your first time fighting? Oh no. If I can
        give you any advice, please tell me.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 666.5, y: 200}
    transitionNode: 0
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: acf0028f-5398-463f-a97f-ebdf8e87f9b1
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Please watch me closely. When I prepare for attacking,
        you can tell by my body movements.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Please DODGE to get out of the way. Then try to hit
        me with your sword.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: You can also try to PARRY my attacks by BLOCKING
        at the correct time.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Parrying leaves me open to your counterattacks. But
        it is harder than dodging.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: If you get disoriented, try using the CAMERA LOCK-ON.
        It keeps your eyes on me.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: I will go easy on you. Unfortunately, I am programmed
        to get stronger as my HP gets lower.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: And don't forget to check the controls. You can find
        them in the pause menu. Just press START or ESC.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1194, y: 202}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: 0a27da67-5dfc-4477-8d0b-40866f563bd6
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: To be honest, it is pretty fun when my rival knows
        what they are doing. I like a tough battle.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: I do not like hurting the helpless.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Sometimes I feel bad for the people paying us so
        much money to fight. But Aya says they deserve it.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: From time to time, some girls defeat me without getting
        help from outside. I think that is really cool.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: But Aya gets really mad when that happens. And I
        never see these girls again on the next day.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1194, y: 433}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  - guid: ac8f7ab0-626a-4f8e-9be2-c796139b2b72
    dialogue:
    - <CharacterName>k__BackingField: Katoro
      <Content>k__BackingField: Please do not let yourself get hurt. I hope you are
        strong.
      <HideCharacter>k__BackingField: 0
      <DialogueEvent>k__BackingField:
        m_PersistentCalls:
          m_Calls: []
    position: {x: 1795.5, y: 292}
    transitionNode: 1
    entryPoint: 0
    isCheckpoint: 0
    disableAlreadyChosenOptions: 0
  <PathToCheckpoint>k__BackingField: 
  <IsNarrativeEndReached>k__BackingField: 0
  <StartFromPreviousNarrativePath>k__BackingField: 1
  <Characters>k__BackingField: []
